If u haven't already, join thousands of other South Africans and tell us about your experience on election day! Dial*120*4729*1#  It's free to dial!

Thanks for volunteering to be a citizen reporter for the 2014 elections! Get started by answering questions or reporting election activity! Dial *120*4729*1# to return to VIP
